29721.title: Global Beats!
29721.description: Tune in for a selection of the biggest Hip-Hop, RnB and Reggaeton beats that are taking over the world!

29722.title: The Rock Zone!
29722.description: You are now entering the rock zone! Expect nothing but the biggest, loudest, hottest rock tunes to ever exist!

29723.title: MTV Unplugged Presents: BTS
29723.description: The global supergroup BTS goes 'Unplugged' to perform not only a few of their latest tracks off BE, but some big surprises as well - all in this can't-miss special.

29724.title: Nick Jonas: MTV World Stage
29724.description: MTV World Stage is your chance to see the biggest artists on the globe live in concert without leaving the comfort of your sofa. Up now, a focus on US artist Nick Jonas.

29725.title: MTV Asks Lewis Capaldi
29725.description: MTV sits down with Lewis Capaldi to get the lowdown on his meteoric rise to the top! Expect some belly laughs, some sentimental stories, and some exclusive music performances.

29726.title: MTV Live: KSI
29726.description: KSI takes Blackpool's iconic Tower Ballroom by storm to celebrate the Switch-On of the World-Famous Blackpool Illuminations, with a set that includes tracks from his chart topping album!

29727.title: HD Hits!
29727.description: We've got big hits and they're even bigger in high def baby!

29728.title: MTV Rewind: 2017
29728.description: Step into the MTV Time Machine and travel back to 2017 to check out what tracks were stealing our hearts and ruling the charts!
